<L>__{exterior cimmerian village day}
<A>__{conan exits the forge only to see the entire village burning. the bodies of everyone he has ever known litter the landscape. nothing stirs. until he hears a strange chopping}
<B>__{sound. the pict}
<A>__{conan spots the pict, who is decapitating a dead cimmerian warrior, adding to the collection of heads at his tattooed waist. the pict doesn't notice as conan slips up behind him, then}
<B>__{runs him through.}
<A>__{as the wide eyed pict dies, conan takes the sword and cuts a notch into his arm.}
